    <item>
      <title>天然气泛滥的欧洲将更多地依赖乌克兰储存</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-01/europe-awash-with-gas-is-set-to-rely-more-on-ukraine-for-storage</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲将用大量天然气结束供暖季，因此在乌克兰储存更多燃料以避免价格暴跌的想法变得越来越有吸引力，尽管此举存在安全风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-01/europe-awash-with-gas-is-set-to-rely-more-on-ukraine-for-storage</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 09:04:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
